title: 133. Trickle Down Liquidation for the Restaurant Industry
description: In this episode of The Barron Report, host Paul Barron sits down with Danielle DiMartino Booth, the chief executive officer and chief strategist for Quill Intelligence LLC. Barron and DiMartino Booth explore finance trends and the future of small businesses.
